§ T11-W11 · 26_HOTFIX_INFRA.csl · architectural blueprint
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

§ THESIS
  apocky.com = manifest-of-truth
  mycelium-peers = byte-CDN
  LoA.exe = polling-verifier-applier-roller-back
  Ed25519 = canonical signing
  Σ-mask = per-user opt-in matrix · default-deny except security.patch
  9 channels × 5 cap-keys × N-1 + N-2 rollback × ¬ DRM

§ AXIOMS  [PRIME_DIRECTIVE encoded]
  N! [harm control surveillance manipulation exploitation
      coercion weaponization discrimination] in-the-doing
  ✓ sovereign-revocable ANY-time · pinned-version-stays-pinned-forever
  ✓ Σ-mask-default-deny except security.patch (cap-D · default-on)
  ✓ rollback-ALWAYS-available · N-1 + N-2 preserved on-disk
  ✓ verify-before-apply · cap-role.of.signer ≡ channel.required_cap()
  ✓ cosmetic-only-axiom : update ¬ change pay-for-power balance unilaterally
  ✗ ¬ DRM · ¬ rootkit · ¬ anti-cheat-spyware

